snippet.title: Diana and Papa Pretend Play with toy Musical Instruments
snippet.description:
Diana and Papa pretend play with Musical Instruments - toys for kids.
Papa is sleeping, and Diana tries to wake him up and uses toys: a drum, a guitar, a piano and other toy musical instruments. Kid even sings nursery rhyme songs, but Dad is still asleep. How the baby was able to wake up Dad, look in this funny video for kids.
